103
00:09:58,780 --> 00:10:01,730
♪You shielded me from the world♪

104
00:10:03,490 --> 00:10:05,940
♪Love has no second chances♪

105
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:09,730
♪I overrated myself♪

106
00:10:14,950 --> 00:10:19,220
♪When our stars cross paths again♪

107
00:10:19,450 --> 00:10:21,970
♪Perhaps it's destiny♪

108
00:10:22,170 --> 00:10:26,420
♪A thousand encounters♪

109
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:29,110
♪All lead to you♪

110
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:32,760
♪My unreasonable demands♪

111
00:10:33,130 --> 00:10:37,170
♪Are precious emotions to you♪

112
00:10:37,450 --> 00:10:42,440
♪I'm sure I am your♪

113
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:44,760
♪Only one♪

114
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:48,210
♪I almost missed you♪

115
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:51,780
♪No one can replace you♪

116
